<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:03:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国总统辩论前亚洲股市震荡；油价创三年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-11/</link><description>由于投资者为美国通胀数据和热切期待的美国总统辩论做准备，亚洲股市周三波动，而由于对需求前景疲弱的担忧，油价徘徊在三年低点附近。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 00:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>游说团体警告欧洲公司怀疑中国是否有可靠的经济复苏计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/european-firms-doubt-china-has-credible-plan-turn-economy-around-lobby-group-2024-09-11/</link><description>欧洲商业游说团体周三表示，在华欧洲企业怀疑中国政府是否有可靠的计划来提振陷入困境的经济的需求，或者是否会实施长期承诺的改革，从而降低了它们在中国的投资兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 00:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/european-firms-doubt-china-has-credible-plan-turn-economy-around-lobby-group-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软，日本9月商业信心创7个月新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-sept-hits-7-month-low-soft-chinese-demand-2024-09-10/</link><description>路透社周三的月度民意调查显示，9月份日本大型制造商的商业信心跌至七个月低点，多个行业的管理者都对中国需求疲软表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 23:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-sept-hits-7-month-low-soft-chinese-demand-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：通货紧缩动态加深</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 21:51:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾特使表示，计划在联合国间隙举行峰会，寻求与中国“讲道理”的方法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/plan-summit-un-sidelines-seek-ways-to-talk-sense-into-china-philippines-envoy-2024-09-10/</link><description>马尼拉驻华盛顿特使周二表示，计划于本月在联合国大会期间举行至少 20 个国家的峰会，寻求途径就中国与菲律宾在南海的对抗问题向中国“讲一些道理”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 21:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/plan-summit-un-sidelines-seek-ways-to-talk-sense-into-china-philippines-envoy-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>iPhone 和竞争对手智能手机的人工智能功能如何叠加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-ai-features-iphone-rival-smartphones-stack-up-2024-09-10/</link><description>苹果在周一的一次活动中为其最新的 iPhone 16 系列推出了一系列人工智能功能，全球智能手机制造商纷纷转向生成式人工智能来鼓励客户升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:40:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-ai-features-iphone-rival-smartphones-stack-up-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰政府表示，ASML 需要获得在中国维修部分设备的许可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-needs-licence-service-some-equipment-china-dutch-government-says-2024-09-10/</link><description>荷兰政府周二澄清，阿斯麦公司需要获得许可证才能为其之前出售给中国客户的计算机芯片制造设备提供备件和软件更新，而这些设备现在受到出口限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-needs-licence-service-some-equipment-china-dutch-government-says-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>星巴克新任首席执行官尼科尔将改善美国门店的咖啡文化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-new-ceo-niccol-focus-us-first-100-days-2024-09-10/</link><description>星巴克新任首席执行官布赖恩·尼科尔(Brian Niccol)表示，在他接掌星巴克的过程中，他将专注于重振该连锁店在美国的咖啡馆文化，因为其昂贵的拿铁咖啡的需求不稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-new-ceo-niccol-focus-us-first-100-days-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国军队将参加巴西与美军联合军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-joins-brazilian-military-exercises-alongside-us-troops-2024-09-10/</link><description>巴西海军周二表示，中国军队本周将首次参加巴西年度军事演习，美国军队也参加了演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-joins-brazilian-military-exercises-alongside-us-troops-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促欧洲对中俄防务关系表示不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-europe-raise-disquiet-over-china-russia-defence-ties-2024-09-10/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二表示，美国敦促其欧洲伙伴更加有力地表达对中国与俄罗斯日益加强的防务合作的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:33:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-europe-raise-disquiet-over-china-russia-defence-ties-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>RTX 看到劳动力挑战，探索中国供应商的替代方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-sees-labor-challenges-exploring-alternatives-china-suppliers-2024-09-10/</link><description>航空航天和国防巨头RTX的负责人在COVID-19大流行之后对全球供应链敲响了警钟，并警告说，为急需的喷气式飞机行业生产线寻找合格的劳动力仍然是一个“巨大”的挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-sees-labor-challenges-exploring-alternatives-china-suppliers-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>台战机执行训练任务海上坠毁 飞行员获救</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-fighter-jet-crashes-sea-training-mission-2024-09-10/</link><description>台湾国防部和官方中央通讯社称，周二晚间，台湾空军一架幻影战斗机在台湾西北海岸坠毁，飞行员成功弹射，获救并被送往医院。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-fighter-jet-crashes-sea-training-mission-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国远景集团将在西班牙投资10亿美元生产绿色氢能机械</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-envision-invest-1-bln-spain-make-green-hydrogen-machinery-2024-09-10/</link><description>西班牙周二表示，已与中国远景集团签署协议，建设一座价值 10 亿美元的工厂，生产用于生产绿色氢气的机械。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 13:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-envision-invest-1-bln-spain-make-green-hydrogen-machinery-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>宝马因大陆制动问题下调 2024 年前景，股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-trims-2024-profit-margin-deliveries-forecast-2024-09-10/</link><description>由于主要中国市场的需求低迷以及大陆集团供应的制动系统出现问题，宝马周二下调了2024年的利润率预期，导致该汽车制造商的股价跌至近两年低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 11:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-trims-2024-profit-margin-deliveries-forecast-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国提议与欧盟谈判解决电动汽车关税争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-proposes-negotiations-with-eu-resolve-electric-vehicle-tariff-dispute-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国再次提出与欧盟委员会就解决经济和贸易摩擦进行谈判，以试图缓解即将对中国制造的电动汽车征收的惩罚性关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-proposes-negotiations-with-eu-resolve-electric-vehicle-tariff-dispute-2024-09-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>